    <briefdescription>
<para>Updates UiTextComponents bound to a <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1mechanics_1_1match_1_1components_1_1LivesComponent" kindref="compound">LivesComponent</ref> via <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1mechanics_1_1match_1_1components_1_1LivesBindingComponent" kindref="compound">LivesBindingComponent</ref>. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Each frame, the system compares the stored <ref refid="namespacehelios_1_1engine_1_1mechanics_1_1match_1_1types_1a5a9b40b91cd49d24dffc892db68cfd6c" kindref="member">LivesRevision</ref> in the binding against the target&apos;s current revision. On mismatch the formatted lives value is written into the UiTextComponent. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
